metadata.description:
After driving away the ghost door, Zi Yang accurately see black robe youth embroidered on the right arm of the pattern, but with the right arm of the ghost door disciples were driven away before, he is the ghost of the door.



At this point, the man in the black robe stopped crying and lay trembling on the ground and dared not get up. Even though the ghost door had already left, he did not dare to move.



Ziyang untied the rope around his neck, and as soon as his hands touched his arms, the man shrank back and knelt on the ground, not daring to look at him.



Zi Yang saw him look trance, then whispered: "you don't be afraid, I won't hurt you. What's your name, by the way?"
